* [http://www.mrtrix.org/ MRtrix website]    <br /><br />
==Setup==
The following changes need to be made to the standard modules before running this software: <br />

<code>module load python/2.7.9</code><br /><code>module load qt/4.8.6/gnu-4.9.2</code><br /><code>module load gsl/1.16/gnu-4.9.2</code><br /><code>module load mrtrix/0.3.12/nogui</code><br /><br />MRtrix has a .mrtrix.conf that is copied to your home directory the first time you run this module from a login node. It sets:

   Analyse.LeftToRight: false
   NumberOfThreads: 4

Alter <code>NumberOfThreads</code> to what you are using in your job script.

=GUI tools unavailable=

<code>mrview</code> and <code>shview</code> in MRtrix 3 cannot be run over a remote X11 connection so are not usable on Legion. To use these tools you will need a local install on your own computer.







